<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Buoina kithiel in ka gam ding zuon ka,
 Khawvel a hin ka tha a muong thei puoi;
 Lalpa siem Salem thak chu thil ingka.

[V2]
 Aw thawhkitna ni lopi thihna zopa,
 Khaw thiengtho a chun ei tun in
 Luigal vangkhuo nuomah,
 Buoi leh thihna zo in zaila sangka.

[V3]
 2. Ka kap hi Lalpa, Na mel mulo in,
 Lunghel do in sunni ka tum zo puoi
 Zion kulhpi, khawilam a um na him?

[V4]
 3. Pielgal ni vak hawih, ka lampi thimah,
 Hung vak inla, Lalpa ka chieh thiem puoi.
 Buoi leh than thim tak hin ei nang viel hi.

[V5]
 4. Ka damlai ni hi thanah pel ingka,
 Mahleh ei ngak nau lam zuon zel ingka,
 Luipi luong gi beihna ah chawl ingka.</lyrics>
<title>Lalpa Siem Salem Thak</title>
<hymn_number>202</hymn_number>
<author>Patea</author>
</song>